Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited I...\NI feel like shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo wee! Canterlot, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I do hope I look festive enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't Canterlot wonderful\Nthis time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wish it was Hearth's\NWarming Eve every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much to look at here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like my durn eyes are gonna\Npop right outta my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play "I spy with my little eye"\Nas we walk. I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I spy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...an eight foot candy cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I spy a snowpony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I spy somepony eating\Na gingerbread house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that\NPrincess Celestia chose us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...to put on the most\Nimportant play of the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know what\Nan honor this is? For all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I wish she hadn't\Nhonored me quite so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on stage. I don't want\Neverypony looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, darling, there is\Nnothing to feel nervous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. All across\NEquestria ponies are preparing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...their own pageants for Hearth's\NWarming Eve in their own towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying they'll be\Ntoo busy to come to our play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no. We're in\Nthe Canterlot pageant...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...the biggest, most important\Nproduction in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of ponies will come to watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe even thousands!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, be a dear and\Nshut those windows, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a reenactment\Nof the founding of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "The Rainbow Dash Show".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it should be "The Rainbow\NDash Show". I'm the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! You've got to\Ncome out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Curtain in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,PIIINKIEEE...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hearth's Warming Eve pageant\Nis about harmony and friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SHUT THE WINDOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, long before\Nthe peaceful rule of Celestia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and before ponies discovered\Nour beautiful land of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...ponies did not know harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a strange and dark time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...a time when ponies\Nwere torn apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...by hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,During this frightful age\Neach of the three tribes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...the pegasi, the unicorns\Nand the earth ponies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...cared not for what befell the other\Ntribes, but only for their own welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In those troubled times, as now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...the pegasi were\Nthe stewards of the weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they demanded\Nsomething in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...food that could only\Nbe grown by the earth ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The unicorns demanded the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...in return for magically\Nbringing forth day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so mistrust between\Nthe tribes festered...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...until one fateful day\Nit came to a boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And what prompted the ponies to clash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,'Twas a mysterious blizzard,\Nthat overtook the land...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...and toppled the tribes'\Nprecarious peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The normally industrious earth ponies\Nwere unable to farm their land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The earth ponies were freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Home of the pegasi fared no better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The pegasi were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the unicorns were\Nfreezing *and* hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the unicorns' magic was\Npowerless against the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Each tribe blamed the others\Nfor their suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the angrier everypony grew,\Nthe worse the blizzard became.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it was decided, that\Na grand summit will be held...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...to figure out a way\Nto cope with the blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Each tribe sent their leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Daughter of the unicorn\Nking: Princess Platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruler of the pegasi:\NCommander Hurricane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly leader of the earth\Nponies: Chancellor Puddinghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the three tribes could\Nfinally settle their differences...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...and agree on a way\Nto get through this disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanna know is why the earth\Nponies are hogging all the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,US?! We're not hogging\Nall the food. You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait. You're right. It's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's only cause you mean old\Npegasuseseses are making it snow like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For the hundredth time, it's not us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not making it snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the unicorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing it with\Ntheir freaky magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you pegasi ruffians, we unicorns\Nwould never stoop to such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-Me-Ph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you non-earths aren't gonna\Nstop using your weirdo powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...to freeze us all, then\NI'm just plum out of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shocker!\NAn earth pony with no ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Hurricane!\NPlease cease with the insults!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the boss of me,\Nyour royal snootiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I BEG YOUR PARDON!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a princess!\NI won't be spoken to that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm leaving first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the blizzard raged on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the summit of the tribes did not\Nturn out as well as hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the three leaders returned\Nhome to lick their wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and basically complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ATTEN-TION!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Aren't you curious\Nabout how it went?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh... Commander Hurricane, sir!\NHow did it go, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Horribly! Those other tribe\Nleaders are so disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they realize that we are\Na mighty tribe of warriors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...and should not be crossed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have got to break ranks\Nwith those weak foals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Clover the Clever! I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, your majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the other pony tribes\Nsee reason as I predicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those other tribes are impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I, for one, can no longer bear to be\Nanywhere near the lowly creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The unicorns are noble and majestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We will no longer consort\Nwith the likes of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it have been easier\Nto use the door, Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe for you, Smart Cookie.\NBut I am a chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was elected, because I know\Nhow to think outside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can also think inside the chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think inside the chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-I...\N-I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh. Hold on to your hooves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just about to be brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided that the earth\Nponies are gonna go it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, so you mean the other\Ntribes didn't come around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot. I really thought we could\Nget through to them if we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones with\Nall the food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually we're all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Then we'll have to go somewhere\Nnear where we can grow some new food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And with me as our fearless\Nleader, what could go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We must find a new land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Private Pansy.\NLet's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup one, hup two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, private!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot let anything distract us\Nfrom the mission at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To find (and if necessary\Nto conquer) a new land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Conquer, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Never know where enemies\Nmight be lurking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any enemies, commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, this is simply taking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My hooves are killing me.\NHow long have we been walking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About five minutes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined finding\Na new land would be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll all be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually think that the three\Ntribes could have tried harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,STOOOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-That is what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, it's just a stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can cross it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to get my gown wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention\Nof arriving at my new land...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...looking like\Na bedraggled earth pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or worse yet,\Na rough-and-tumble pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I, for one, have no intention\Nof stooping down to their level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I have no trouble\Nwatching *you* stoop down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And do watch the gown, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth more than all\Nof the books in your library.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible! Are you suggesting\Nthat I'm reading the map wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not, your chancellorness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that there are\Nholes in the map and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! How else could I\Nsee where I was going!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or talk? I need to be able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how would we survive\Nif I just only shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven forbid that should happen,\Nyour chancellorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that the map\Nis also upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a news flash for you, Cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The earth is round.\NThere is no up or down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a relief to me, that\Nyou're in charge of this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Relief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need relief! If anypony\Nneeds relief around here, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a chancellor! I'm a big shot.\NYou're just my, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You take the map, while\NI enjoy some relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, chancellor Puddinghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And so each leader encountered\Nobstacles along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But eventually they all arrived\Nin the new and wondrous land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony ever seen paradise before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the new land\Nwe've been searching for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a view. I can see\Nmy future house from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I proclaim this new land to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegasopolis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This ruby is dazzling.\NThis whole land is dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm double-dazzled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the unicorns\NI hereby dub this land Unicornia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The air! The trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The dirt. This dirt is the dirtiest\Ndirt in the whole dirt world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And fertile too.\NPerfect to grow on food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the earth ponies,\NI think I'm gonna call this new place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirtville!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations to me\Nfor thinking of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found our new home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted my flag first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did not!\N-Did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted mine earlier than first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you riffraff\Nare trespassing in Unicornia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Pegasopolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Earth!\N-Pegasopolis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we fight for the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,May the best pony win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Clover the Clever, throw\Nthat brute into the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What dungeon?! Look.\NPerhaps if we all calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. Let's all calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I vote for calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you court-martialled\Nfor insubordination, private!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We settle this on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dares throw a snowball at royalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Where'd all this\Nsnow come from anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the paradise that the ponies\Nhad found was soon lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...buried beneath a thick blanket\Nof snow and hard feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of beautiful, it was blizzardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of wonderful, it was wintery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of spectacular,\Nit was snowtacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Instead of...\N-We get it! Move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony was forced to seek shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They searched high and low...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the only shelter for miles\Nwas a cold and desolate cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the three\Ntribes had to share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And nopony was too happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Commander Hothead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Commander Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Commander, could you just\Nstand back and give me my royal space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean like this, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see this invisible line?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Private, outline our territory\Nfor everypony to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See this real, non-invisible line?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No unicorns or earth ponies\Nare allowed to cross it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sovereign\Nterritory of Pegasopolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Clover the Clever!\N-Smart Cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go around the rock. Go over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up an inch\Nof territory to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That rock is clearly on the Unicornia's\Nside of the cave and it belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? There could be jewels inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I claim this rock for Pegasopolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhand that rock this\Ninstant, you scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lookie, found my rock.\NI've been looking for it everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You invaded our territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Finders keepers, losers weepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me my rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everypony! The entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Now there's\Nno way out. We're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You two deserve this horrible fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing but argue\Nand fight with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been fighting too,\N"Your Highness".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been fighting\Nnearly as much as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A unicorn never stoops to fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just cause you wimpy\Nunicorns know you never win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth ponies are numbskul...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegasi are brut...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicorns are snob...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be... windigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Windigos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My mentor, Star Swirl the Bearded,\Ntaught me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're winter spirits that feed\Non fighting and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The more hate the spirit feels,\Nthe colder things become.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We, three tribes. We brought\Nthis blizzard to our home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...by fightin' and\Nnot trustin' each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's destroyin' this land too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now our bodies will\Nbecome as cold as our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All because we were\Nfoolish enough to hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually hate Commander Hurricane\Na lot more than I hate you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't really hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just really, really,\Nreally, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...really, really, really,\Nreally, really dislike her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, I don't hate you guys either.\N-Nor do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what our differences,\Nwe're all ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know unicorns could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like this has\Never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know it couldn't\Nhave been just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from all three of us\Njoin together in friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All through the night the three ponies\Nkept the fire of friendship alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...by telling stories to one another\Nand by singing songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...which of course became the winter\Ncarols that we all still sing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually the warmth of the\Nfire and singing and laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...reached the leaders and\Ntheir bodies began to thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it even began to melt their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The three leaders agreed to\Nshare the beautiful land...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and with it harmony,\Never afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...and together they\Nnamed their new land...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fire of friendship\Nlives in our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as it burns,\Nwe cannot drift apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though quarrels arise,\Ntheir numbers are few{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Laughter and singing will see us through\N(Will see us through){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are a circle of pony friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A circle of friends\Nwe'll be to the very end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be so honored that\NPrincess Celestia chose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She must really think we exemplify\Nwhat good friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, I thought you\Nclosed all the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash should have flown up there\Nand shut it. After all, she's got wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I always have to do\Nall the high-up chores?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't Twilight use\Nher magic for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
